U.K. stocks erased gains, leaving
the benchmark FTSE 100 Index little changed. The gauge rose less
than 0.1 percent to 5,388.60 as of 11:08 a.m. in  London . The
measure has swung between losses of as much as 0.8 percent and
an advance of 0.4 percent today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
